{"tid":1801361,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"和你shop 2.0 之 真-和你shop","createTime":"2019-12-28T14:39:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-29T02:32:22.000Z","uid":8170,"like":11,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"4d641b1ca5056e24d255faddb701fd4db1040952","tid":1801361,"uid":8170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T14:39:32.000Z","msg":"基本上係研究咗之前和你shop同塞機場塞鐵之後嘅改進版，幾項要點：<br />\n1. 不要 blackbloc，不要 blackbloc，不要 blackbloc，一般港豬 look 簡單服飾，易撞嘅衫例如 Uniqlo 淨色 Tea / 風褸<br />\n<strong>原因：自己TAG自己做目標人物</strong><br />\n2. 忍口！忍口！忍口！唔好叫口號、唔好唱榮光、最最最重要，唔好撚狗包括便衣狗，齋行，排隊，睇下唔買<br />\n<strong>原因：扮港豬，你有冇見過港豬商場會叫口號唱歌？又係自 TAG 之舉</strong><br />\n3. 有狗進場，有舖準備關門即可低調走人，仲有！走時唔駛叫，唔駛叫，唔駛叫。<br />\n<strong>原因：狗進咗場，港豬仲會 shopping 咩？咁目標已經完咗一大半，關埋商場就成功，之後開返？你會唔會出去商場出面等佢開返？冇人會囉。</strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">最後，唔好講咩又唔叫又唔唱又唔裝修「咁不如返屋企」，你要刷存在感刷成功感係你時之快。正所謂屌狗一時爽，勇武少一人。忍口啦！</span></span>"},{"pid":"f5d56af626251da93bd4e6339d8d889199b4e73a","tid":1801361,"uid":242323,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T15:05:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3d8b5468aa24bf59e8afe71042d0463e3728320","tid":1801361,"uid":68689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T15:10:31.000Z","msg":"咁咪比林鄭入天下太平 已經成功止暴制亂<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"193ed1af1bf9e23a8eb9af80af565a8eefeab03d","tid":1801361,"uid":8170,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e3d8b5468aa24bf59e8afe71042d0463e3728320","tid":1801361,"uid":68689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T15:10:31.000Z","msg":"咁咪比林鄭入天下太平 已經成功止暴制亂<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T15:13:04.000Z","msg":"表面上太平咗，實際上個商場死咗。"},{"pid":"7e517f886b4d91e0c43c5c71245a0af301f27711","tid":1801361,"uid":327462,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e3